 * \brief Returns the direction of the hero&apos;s movement as defined by the controls applied by the player
 * and the movements allowed is the current state.
 *
 * If he is not moving, -1 is returned.
 * This direction may be different from the real movement direction because of obstacles.
 *
 * \return the hero&apos;s wanted direction between 0 and 7, or -1 if he is stopped
